<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1457671>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Gryposuchus jessei holotype (unnumbered). (a, b) Gryposuchus jessei holotype drawings based on piCtures and from the original paper (GüriCh, 1912), in ventral and dorsal view respeCtively. SCale bar = 50mm. Refer to the main text for the abbreviations list." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1457671/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1457673>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Gryposuchus jessei, referred speCimen (UFAC 1272). (a, b) ventral and dorsal view respeCtively; (c) zoom at the first maxillary teeth of the right maxilla. SCale bar = 50mm. Refer to the main text for the abbreviations list." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1457673/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1457675>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Gryposuchus speCies in dorsal view. MorphologiCal variations at the external naris, premaxilla-maxilla suture and bones. (a) Gryposuchus jessei (unnumbered holotype); (b) Gryposuchus jessei (UFAC 1272); (c) Gryposuchus pachakamue (MUSM 1981); (d) Gryposuchus neogaeus (MLP 26-413); (e) Gryposuchus colombianus (IGM 184696); and, (f) Gryposuchus croizati (AMU-CURS-58). SCale bars: 50mm. Numbers represent the Corresponding maxillary teeth whiCh is aligned with the posterior wedge-shaped proCess of premaxilla." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1457675/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1457677>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Gryposuchus speCies in ventral view. MorphologiCal variations at the inCisive foramen, alveolar size and distribution, premaxilla-maxilla suture and bone. (a) Gryposuchus jessei (unnumbered holotype); (b) Gryposuchus jessei (UFAC 1272); (c) Gryposuchus neogaeus (MLP 26-413); (d) Gryposuchus croizati (AMU-CURS-58); (e) Gryposuchus pachakamue (MUSM 1981). SCale bars: 50mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1457677/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1457669>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Map of the speCimens loCalities. a) Map of South AmeriCa indiCating the region were the Gryposuchus jessei holotype and UFAC 1272 was found in blaCk box; b) Zoom in the blaCk box area, F-2 Corresponding to type loCality of Gryposuchus jessei, and the Sena Madureira muniCipality were UFAC 1272 was ColleCted. Modified from Hsiou et al. 2009." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1457669/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

